query:
SELECT gat.token, gat.isActive, gp.name, gp.id as gpId
FROM gp_access_tokens gat 
JOIN game_presenters gp ON gat.gamePresenterId = gp.id 
WHERE gat.isActive = 1
LIMIT 10;
